aiops-k8s-07': ['shippingservice-1', 'frontend-1', 'emailservice-0', 'currencyservice-2', 'adservice-1', 'cartservice-0', 'currencyservice-1'], 'aiops-k8s-08': ['recommendationservice-0', 'redis-cart-0', 'productcatalogservice-0', 'paymentservice-0', 'cartservice-2', 'adservice-2', 'checkoutservice-2', 'frontend-2', 'currencyservice-2']}\n\n\n[ANALYSIS STATE]\n\nCurrent Hypothesis: None\n\nCurrent Iteration: 2\n\n\n[AGENT FINDINGS HISTORY]\n\n--- Log Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的日志数据，我现在进行故障分析。让我分析这些错误日志并提取关键信息。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Unavailable\", \"timed out\", \"shipping error\", \"shipping quote failure\", \"server handshake\", \"ClassNotFoundException\", \"OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice 出现 Unavailable 和 timed out 错误，导致无法完成服务器握手，影响订单处理\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = shipping error: shipment failed: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice 出现 ClassNotFoundException 错误，OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector 类加载失败，可能影响监控和追踪功能\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Could not create ContextDataInjector for 'io.opencensus.contrib.logcorrelation.log4j2.OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector', using default org.apache.logging.log4j.core.impl.ThreadContextDataInjector$ForCopyOnWriteThreadContextMap: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: io.opencensus.contrib.logcorrelation.log4j2.OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **主要故障模式**：shippingservice 出现 RPC 连接超时和不可用错误，这是影响订单处理的主要根因\n2. **次要问题**：adservice 存在类加载问题，但这是次要的监控配置问题\n3. **时间模式**：故障发生在 10:11 和 10:25 两个时间点，表明可能是间歇性故障\n4. **影响范围**：frontend 服务受到影响，无法完成订单处理流程\n\nshippingservice 的连接超时问题很可能是本次故障的主要根因，需要进一步调查该服务的状态和资源使用情况。\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的指标数据，我对故障期间的系统