析调用链中的异常模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice的GetQuote操作从正常的9415ms激增至1030857ms（延迟倍数109.5倍），ShipOrder操作从14434ms激增至2513904ms（延迟倍数174.2倍），出现超时握手错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"作为shippingservice的上游调用方，checkoutservice因下游超时导致PlaceOrder操作延迟从154721ms增至2187982ms（延迟倍数14.1倍），并产生shipping error错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务因checkoutservice异常导致HTTP 500错误，推荐服务调用延迟从118341ms激增至2732470ms（延迟倍数23.1倍）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现分析：**\n\n1. **根因服务识别**：`shippingservice` 是明确的根因服务，其操作延迟激增100-170倍，并产生\"timed out waiting for server handshake\"错误，表明服务无法正常处理请求。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - shippingservice (根因) → checkoutservice (受害者) → frontend (最终影响)\n   - 错误状态码显示shippingservice的超时错误向上传播\n\n3. **延迟特征**：\n   - shippingservice的GetQuote和ShipOrder操作延迟异常显著\n   - 超时握手错误表明网络连接或服务处理能力问题\n   - 其他服务（如cartservice、productcatalogservice）也有轻微延迟，但属于次要影响\n\n4. **拓扑验证**：符合系统架构中checkoutservice依赖shippingservice的调用关系，因果关系明确。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "70d3b8b0-329", "component": "shippingservice", "reason": "rrt_max and rrt spike causing timed out waiting for server handshake errors in s